note hollow-square.vrb — hollow square border.
note Only the first/last row and first/last column print *.

ask the user "square size?" and save to size.

row = 1.
while row <= size:
    col = 1.
    while col <= size:
        if row == 1 or row == size or col == 1 or col == size:
            display "*".
        else:
            display " ".
        end.
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row += 1.
end.
